{"tid":458594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★發展局局長：建造機電行業求才若渴，冀未來有更多青年人加入","createTime":"2017-11-05T04:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T15:20:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c6bbcb38a5272298e5e1b50d25480c7d9fe24ab6","tid":458594,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"建造業或機電行業均求才若渴，冀有更多青年人入行，並透過持續在職培訓，應付業內人手短缺問題。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，政府自2010年起已<span style=\"color: red;\">撥款合共4億2千萬元</span>，支持建造業議會加強對本地建造業人員的培訓；議會亦於2017年4月實施建造業工人「專工專責」，為業界從業員建立有系統的晉升階梯，提供職業發展機會，吸引更多新人入行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/131039/4成建造業技工10年內退休-黃偉綸-設晉升階梯-吸引青年人入行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F131039%2F4%E6%88%90%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A510%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-%E9%BB%83%E5%81%89%E7%B6%B8-%E8%A8%AD%E6%99%89%E5%8D%87%E9%9A%8E%E6%A2%AF-%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%8C&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f0bfb02f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/131039/4成建造業技工10年內退休-黃偉綸-設晉升階梯-吸引青年人入行</a>"},{"pid":"fd7a27bfdf5b53c27ec3b3cfc391059c3eab342b","tid":458594,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"撥款合共4億2千萬元<br />\n撥款合共4億2千萬元<br />\n撥款合共4億2千萬元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhere is the money?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e57f7271d14c7b15a4c8834e174a1f0466eeaf","tid":458594,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/956226/xlarge/c9fc904b0c27e9715c3eae95e8d2f0bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F956226%2Fxlarge%2Fc9fc904b0c27e9715c3eae95e8d2f0bc.jpg&h=93030958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37843d055c98816b28736f95b7fd02cbb4cf4a46","tid":458594,"uid":90,"like":